headline: EastGroup Properties (EGP) Lags Q4 FFO and Revenue Estimates
summary: EastGroup Properties (EGP) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of -0.46% and 1.49%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
